- Waitgroup is kind of a modified version of the time.sleep, when use this waitgroup we have 3 jobs to to be done
1. add that means as soon as a go routine is being created we have to add that into this waitgroup so that it is responsible for management, for example we have five go routines and until unless they are back it will not end 
2. done - once your job is done and that go routine whatever you have sent is done with its work then it is your responsibility to call for done
3. wait - whenever my job is not done it should wait

